{"word":"ἀλλήλων","slug":"ἀλλήλων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀλλήλων</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄλλος\">ἄλλος</a></el>] (no nominative of this reciprocal pronoun, hence the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> is here used as the headword) <b><i>each other, one another:</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:520 2:15'>Ro 2:15</a>; <a href='B:520 12:5'>12:5</a>; <a href='B:550 6:2'>Gal 6:2</a>; <a href='B:560 4:25'>Eph 4:25</a>; <a href='B:660 4:11'>Js 4:11</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀλλήλοις\">ἀλλήλοις</a></el><b> <a href='B:510 19:38'>Ac 19:38</a>; <a href='B:550 5:17'>Gal 5:17</a>; <a href='B:480 9:50'>Mk 9:50</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a></el>); <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀλλήλους\">ἀλλήλους</a></el><b> <a href='B:500 13:34'>J 13:34</a>; <a href='B:520 13:8'>Ro 13:8</a>; <a href='B:500 13:22'>J 13:22</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a></el>). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλλήλους\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλλογενής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}